🔹 Procedure Question

❓ Write a procedure to accept two numbers and find minimum and maximum from two numbers.


---

✅ Procedure

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE min_max(a INT, b INT)
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $$
DECLARE
    min_val INT;
    max_val INT;
BEGIN
    IF a > b THEN
        max_val := a;
        min_val := b;
    ELSE
        max_val := b;
        min_val := a;
    END IF;

    RAISE NOTICE 'Minimum = %, Maximum = %', min_val, max_val;
END;
$$;


